  <summary date="2021-11-03T10:41:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Smarter Pretrial Detention for Drug Charges Act of 2021

This bill removes the presumption of pretrial detention for an individual who is charged with a federal drug offense for which the maximum term of imprisonment is 10 years or more.</summary>
